definedTerms.definition:
means:
(a) a deformity of a joint of a vertebra;
(b) a deformity of a vertebra;
(c) a kyphotic abnormality;
(d) a lordotic abnormality;
(e) necrosis of bone;
(f) retrospondylolisthesis;
(g) scoliosis; or
(h) spondylolisthesis

